metadata.name: trashie 203
metadata.description: Each trashie was carefully curated from a vast creation of AI generated images. The imperfections intentionally remain to mark this moment of time for art generated through thoughtful prompting. Caricatures, references, and homages are all satire. Enjoy the fun and wonder of a world past, present, and future where our trash cans have lives of their own as they serve our needs without complaint. CC0, remix at will.
